              <header>
                  <h1 property="dc:title" datatype="" class="article-title">
            <a href="/web/20140409050542/http://www.pressgazette.co.uk/new-editors-independent-and-i-newspapers" rel="bookmark">Amol Rajan is made editor of The Independent as Chris Blackhurst becomes group content director</a>
